first-quarter loss and rose 6 7/8 to 110 5/8.
</P>
<P>
   Declining issues outnumbered advancers by a 2-to-1 margin on the
New York Stock Exchange, where volume came to 369.65 million
shares, ahead of Wednesday's pace.
</P>
<P>
   The Russell 2000 index fell 1.20 to 483.04.
</P>
