1999 season before being released Sept. 17. He joined the Lions
after playing earlier last year for the Berlin Thunder of NFL
Europe.
</P>
<P>
   Alexander, selected by Washington in the seventh round of the
1999 draft, was released Sept. 2 by the Redskins after training
camp. The San Diego Chargers signed him Nov. 24 to their practice
squad, where he spent the final six weeks of the season.
</P>
