<HEADLINE> Fire Sale Queen in Senorita Stakes  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   INGLEWOOD, Calif. (AP) -- Fire Sale Queen highlights a field of
10 entries in Friday night's $100,000-added Senorita Stakes at
Hollywood Park.
</P>
<P>
   Fire Sale Queen will be ridden by Frank Alvarado and carry 118
pounds in the one-mile race for 3-year-old fillies on turf as
Hollywood Park opens its 65-day thoroughbred racing season. Each of
the other nine entries was assigned 114 pounds.
</P>
