   The opening weekend at Hollywood Park will be capped by the
inaugural California Gold Rush on Sunday -- a series of 10 stakes
races exclusively for California-breds with gross purses totaling
$1.26 million. The feature race at 1[ miles is the $250,000 Snow
Chief Stakes.
</P>
